    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/>Ego <persName xml:lang="la">Gerontia</persName> arcam de proprio
                    <lb n="2"/><seg xml:id="seg1">com<supplied reason="lost">para</supplied>vi. Si qu<supplied reason="lost">is eam aperi</supplied><unclear>r</unclear>e</seg>
                    <lb n="3"/>voluerit dabit fisco <measure type="fine" unit="roman_pound" commodity="silver" quantity="5"><expan><abbr>arg</abbr><ex>enti</ex></expan> pondo <num value="5">V</num></measure>.
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app loc="2" from="#seg1">
                        <lem>com<supplied reason="lost">para</supplied>vi. Si qu<supplied reason="lost">is eam aperi</supplied><unclear>r</unclear>e</lem>
                        <rdg source="#bertolini1875a #bertolini1875b #cilv8765 #ilcv818a #edr097913">
                            com<supplied reason="lost">paravi mihi. Si quis eam</supplied> aperire
                        </rdg>
                    </app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <p>
                    I, <persName ref="#gerontia" xml:lang="la">Gerontia</persName>, prepared the sarcophagus with my own funds.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Whoever wishes to open it shall give to the <term xml:lang="la">fiscus</term> 5 roman pounds of silver.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it">
                <p>Io, <persName ref="#gerontia" xml:lang="la">Gerontia</persName>, ho comprato l'arca con i miei propri fondi.</p>
                <p>Se qualcuno vorrà aprirla, verserà al fisco cinque libbre d'argento.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" xml:lang="en">
                <p><persName xml:lang="la">Gerontia</persName> is a name of Greek origin, coming from Asia Minor (<ref target="../references/bibliography.xml#holder">Holder 1904, 2014</ref>).</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" xml:lang="it">
                <p><persName xml:lang="la">Gerontia</persName> è un nome di origine greca, proveniente dall’Asia Minore (<ref target="../references/bibliography.xml#holder">Holder 1904, 2014</ref>).</p>
            </div>
